21 this section.
22 “(c) The amount of the assessments provided for under subsections (2) and (3) of this
23 section shall be computed using the assessment rates determined under subsections (5) and
24 (6) of this section.
25 “(d) The assessment rates under subsections (5) and (6) of this section shall be deter-
26 mined separately.
