17 “(7)(a) If the department determines that the balance of the Workers’ Benefit Fund will fall
18 below the balance required under [this] subsection (5) of this section, the department shall devise
19 and report to the Workers’ Compensation Management-Labor Advisory Committee a plan to increase
20 the balance to the required amount.
