40 “[(7)] (10)(a) There is established a Retroactive Program for the purpose of providing increased
41 benefits to claimants or beneficiaries eligible to receive compensation under the benefit schedules
42 of ORS 656.204, 656.206, 656.208 and 656.210 that are lower than currently being paid for like inju-
43 ries. However, benefits payable under ORS 656.210 may not be increased by the Retroactive Program
44 for claimants whose injury occurred on or after April 1, 1974.
45 “(b) Notwithstanding the formulas for computing benefits provided in ORS 656.204, 656.206,
